      "content": "but that's the thing, the doctor says the greens will mess up the warfarin, but if i'm not taking the warfarin anymore, then the greens wouldn't be \"messing it up\" they would just be doing the job, right? if i just gradually taper off the pills while increasing my garlic and spinach intake, wouldn't that be a smooth transition? i just want to know if there's a specific amount of garlic or how many smoothies i should aim for to make sure i stay thin enough without the meds.",
